def has_bowls_in_dishwasher(dishwasher:item):
    # Function to check if bowls are in the dishwasher
    symbol has_bowls=exists o: item : is_bowl(o) and inside(o, dishwasher)
    return has_bowls

behavior find_plates():
    body:
        foreach o: item:
            if is_plate(o) and not visited(o):
                observe(o, "Check if the plate needs washing")

behavior load_plates_into_dishwasher(plate:item, dishwasher:item):

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:

        # Select a dish washer
        if has_bowls_in_dishwasher(dishwasher):
